articles.title: ENG vs AUS, 4th Test highlights: Rain washes out Day 5 as AUS retain Ashes - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Australia have retained the Ashes after the fourth Test at Old Trafford ended in a draw on Sunday with no play possible on Day 5 of the penultimate encounter.
